{"id":2005,"date":"2022-04-01T18:42:49","date_gmt":"2022-04-01T16:42:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/?page_id=2005"},"modified":"2022-05-01T20:57:49","modified_gmt":"2022-05-01T18:57:49","slug":"2002-os-caminos-novos-de-simon-young","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/2002-os-caminos-novos-de-simon-young\/","title":{"rendered":"Os cami\u00f1os novos de Simon Young (2002)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>No ano 2002, o ingl\u00e9s Simon Young publicou &#8220;Britonia: Cami\u00f1os novos&#8221; (ToxosOutos), un traballo froito de ano e medio de investigaci\u00f3n sobre o pasado da diocese britoniense. En 2004 aparecer\u00eda traducido ao castel\u00e1n na mesma editorial.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">&#8220;Este \u00e9 un estudio sobre Britonia, un asentamento celto-brit\u00e1nico do noroeste da Pen\u00ednsula no alto medievo. Moitos historiadores de calidade como, por exemplo, Pierre David e Antonio Garc\u00eda y Garc\u00eda, aportaron valiosas contribuci\u00f3ns sobre Britonia. Pero a tese deste libro \u00e9 que o corpus establecido por estes especialistas \u00e9 limitado. Neste traballo, o autor, combinando elementos da civilizaci\u00f3n celto-brit\u00e1nica e do medievo galego, ach\u00e9gase a esta \u00e1rea xa ben explorada da historia a trav\u00e9s de rutas pouco usuais e inesperadas: a toponimia, a antroponimia, o folclore, documentaci\u00f3n medieval anteriormente desatendida e a comparaci\u00f3n coa di\u00e1spora celto-brit\u00e1nica noutras rexi\u00f3ns de Europa. O libro est\u00e1 dividido en tres partes. Na parte 1 exam\u00ednanse as fontes tradicionais sobre o asentamento. A parte 2 presenta novas fontes de estudio. A parte 3 \u00e9 unha interpretaci\u00f3n provocativa das fontes utilizadas tanto na primeira como na segunda parte. Os ap\u00e9ndices incl\u00faen unha reproducci\u00f3n do traballo do Padre Fl\u00f3rez sobre a diocese de Britonia&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-container-2 wp-block-gallery-1 wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"564\" height=\"850\" data-id=\"2018\"  src=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-nuevos-portada-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2018\" srcset=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-nuevos-portada-1.jpg 564w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-nuevos-portada-1-199x300.jpg 199w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-nuevos-portada-1-8x12.jpg 8w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"670\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"2007\"  src=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-novos-670x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2007\" srcset=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-novos-670x1024.jpg 670w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-novos-196x300.jpg 196w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-novos-768x1173.jpg 768w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-novos-8x12.jpg 8w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Britonia.-Caminos-novos.jpg 950w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Durante este tempo dedicado aos asentamentos dos brit\u00f3ns do Noroeste peninsular, Simon Young mantivo activa unha p\u00e1xina web onde subiu alg\u00fans dos seus resultados: The Britonian Studies Internet Resource. Hoxe at\u00f3pase arquivada: <a href=\"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20060617211626\/http:\/www.britonia.fsnet.co.uk\/index.html\">Britonia (archive.org)<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Outros traballos do mesmo autor sobre este tema son:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><object class=\"wp-block-file__embed\" data=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2003-The-Bishops-of-the-early-medieval-diocese-of-Britonia.pdf\" type=\"application\/pdf\" style=\"width:100%;height:600px\" aria-label=\"Incrustado de Simon-Young-2003-The-Bishops-of-the-early-medieval-diocese-of-Britonia.\"><\/object><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-72b83215-4a02-4f28-b3f0-6045c4ee00a6\" href=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2003-The-Bishops-of-the-early-medieval-diocese-of-Britonia.pdf\">Simon-Young-2003-The-Bishops-of-the-early-medieval-diocese-of-Britonia<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2003-The-Bishops-of-the-early-medieval-diocese-of-Britonia.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-72b83215-4a02-4f28-b3f0-6045c4ee00a6\">Descarga<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><object class=\"wp-block-file__embed\" data=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Iberian-Addenda-to-Fleuriots-Toponymes.pdf\" type=\"application\/pdf\" style=\"width:100%;height:600px\" aria-label=\"Incrustado de Simon-Young-2002-Iberian-Addenda-to-Fleuriots-Toponymes.\"><\/object><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-353249c2-7834-43d1-80fc-c88c88eff2a5\" href=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Iberian-Addenda-to-Fleuriots-Toponymes.pdf\">Simon-Young-2002-Iberian-Addenda-to-Fleuriots-Toponymes<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Simon-Young-2002-Iberian-Addenda-to-Fleuriots-Toponymes.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-353249c2-7834-43d1-80fc-c88c88eff2a5\">Descarga<\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{